<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= title || 'Manutenzione | B4US' %></title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Outfit:wght@600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            primary: "#28a745",
            secondary: "#4a4a4a",
          },
          fontFamily: {
            sans: ["Inter", "sans-serif"],
            display: ["Outfit", "sans-serif"],
          },
        },
      },
    };
  </script>
  <style>
    .hero-pattern {
      background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 2px 2px, rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.08) 1px, transparent 0);
      background-size: 32px 32px;
    }
    .gear-spin {
      animation: gear-spin 4s linear infinite;
    }
    @keyframes gear-spin {
      from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
      to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-50 text-secondary font-sans flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 hero-pattern">
  <div class="max-w-lg w-full text-center">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl bg-primary/10 text-primary mb-8 gear-spin">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.343 3.94c.09-.542.56-.94 1.11-.94h1.093c.55 0 1.02.398 1.11.94l.149.894c.07.424.384.764.78.93.398.164.855.142 1.205-.108l.737-.493a1.125 1.125 0 0 1 1.45.494l.073.082a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-.494 1.45l-.493.737c-.25.35-.272.806-.107 1.204.165.397.505.71.93.78l.893.15c.543.09.94.56.94 1.109v1.094c0 .55-.397 1.02-.94 1.11l-.893.149c-.425.07-.765.383-.93.78-.165.398-.143.854.107 1.204l.493.738a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-.494 1.45l-.073.081a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.45.494l-.738-.493c-.35-.25-.806-.272-1.204-.107-.397.165-.71.505-.78.929l-.15.894c-.09.542-.56.94-1.11.94h-1.094c-.55 0-1.019-.398-1.11-.94l-.148-.894c-.071-.424-.384-.764-.781-.93-.398-.164-.854-.142-1.204.108l-.738.493a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.449-.494l-.083-.073a1.125 1.125 0 0 1 .494-1.45l.493-.737c.25-.35.273-.806.108-1.204-.165-.397-.505-.71-.93-.78l-.894-.15C4.398 13.99 4 13.52 4 12.97v-1.094c0-.55.398-1.02.94-1.11l.894-.15c.424-.07.765-.383.93-.78.165-.398.143-.854-.107-1.204l-.493-.738a1.125 1.125 0 0 1 .494-1.45l.073-.082a1.125 1.125 0 0 1 1.45.494l.493.737c.35.25.807.272 1.204.107.397-.165.71-.505.78-.929l.15-.894z" />
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 12a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0z" />
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">
      Manutenzione in corso
    </h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
      Stiamo aggiornando il sito per offrirti un'esperienza migliore. Torneremo online a breve.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-10">
      Grazie per la pazienza.
    </p>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-primary font-semibold">
      <span class="font-display text-xl">B4US</span>
      <span class="text-gray-400">|</span>
      <span>Simplify IT</span>
    </div>
    <button type="button" onclick="window.location.reload()" class="mt-10 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-primary bg-primary/10 rounded-xl hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15" /></svg>
      Riprova
    </button>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
